.SH "NAME"
rio_add_outb_message \- Add RIO message to an outbound mailbox queue
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP \w'int\ rio_add_outb_message('u
.BI "int rio_add_outb_message(struct\ rio_mport\ *\ " "mport" ", struct\ rio_dev\ *\ " "rdev" ", int\ " "mbox" ", void\ *\ " "buffer" ", size_t\ " "len" ");"
.SH "ARGUMENTS"
.PP
\fImport\fR
.RS 4
RIO master port containing the outbound queue
.RE
.PP
\fIrdev\fR
.RS 4
RIO device the message is be sent to
.RE
.PP
\fImbox\fR
.RS 4
The outbound mailbox queue
.RE
.PP
\fIbuffer\fR
.RS 4
Pointer to the message buffer
.RE
.PP
\fIlen\fR
.RS 4
Length of the message buffer
.RE
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
Adds a RIO message buffer to an outbound mailbox queue for transmission\&. Returns 0 on success\&.
